rated in years. HIGHLY RECOMMEND!"}},"step_gnARCT":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Jessica Z.","filter_tag":"eczema","line_1_text":"Worked Epic On My Sensitive Skin","line_2_text":"Deep moisturizer. A little goes a long ways. Brought down redness, helped heal a bad eczema flare within a few days. Relief from tightness, burning and flakes was immediate."}},"step_CdejB3":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Brooke B.","filter_tag":"acne","line_1_text":"My Acne Is Healing Up!","line_2_text":"I've only used it for 2 days and I'd have to say, my acne is healing up. It smells nice as well"}},"step_w8PQKT":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Juanita M.","filter_tag":"acne","line_1_text":"Doesn't Clog Your Pores","line_2_text":"It leaves your skin feeling so soft and it doesn’t clog your pores! It doesn't look like a greasy mess"}},"step_qDVTLm":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Nicole P.","filter_tag":"acne","line_1_text":"It Turned My Skin Around","line_2_text":"My skin is not as dry or chapped. It hasn't cause any sort of irritation or breakouts. I'm very happy with the products and even used a little on my 4 month old as well for some drool rash"}},"step_RjPrmq":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Courtney T.","filter_tag":"eczema","line_1_text":"Will Definitely Buy Again","line_2_text":"A little goes a long way. It helped clear my son’s eczema. I also use it on my face as a daily moisturizer. It’s not greasy and absorbs well into my skin without leaving my face shiny. Overall great product"}},"step_zUGjer":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Raven P.","filter_tag":"eczema","line_1_text":"I Can't Live Without It","line_2_text":"I struggled for 30 years with eczema, sensitive, and extremely dry cracking\/flaking skin. This product changed my life and with only one ingredient"}},"step_XC7pzT":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Danielle B.","filter_tag":"anti-aging","line_1_text":"No One Can Guess My Age","line_2_text":"My fine lines have decreased by at least 75% and my discoloration sun spots have lightened. I refuse to use anything else on my face\/neck\/chest. Absolutely recommend."}},"step_3VyMmi":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Frank A.","filter_tag":"dry","line_1_text":"You Have To Try This!","line_2_text":"\"I have been in search of a product for my dry itchy cracked skin. After only one week of applying this to my hands my arms my legs my feet and my lips - I still can't believe how good this product is."}},"step_hPJ4Cd":{"type":"step","settings":{"step_title":"Kim M.","filter_tag":"dry","line_1_text":"No Smell, Glided On Smoothly","line_2_text":"I love the texture and appreciate that there is no smell. It glided on smoothly and had absorbed into my skin by morning. Great product!"}}},"block_order":["step_GjTqGU","step_Fgayae","step_tJ9NaJ","step_gnARCT","step_CdejB3","step_w8PQKT","step_qDVTLm","step_RjPrmq","step_zUGjer","step_XC7pzT","step_3VyMmi","step_hPJ4Cd"],"name":"HT Review Slider","settings":{"show_trust_badge":true,"star_color":"#ff8a00","review_text_color":"#ffffff","reference_product":"the-everyday-jar","review_boost":0,"override_avg":"","review_text":"[avg]\/5 average across thousands of orders","main_title":"Made For Everyone","sub_title":"Real results from real people who have transformed their skin. A few of our favorites below"}},"ht_landingpage_pack_selector_c4QE3e":{"type":"ht-landingpage-pack-selector","name":"Marble Bundle Selector","settings":{"product":"the-everyday-jar","heading":"Stock Up & Save","subtext":"Want More Than  1? First jar is still $10. Secure your supply and save up to 25% when you choose a multi-pack today.","badge_1":"LIMITED OFFER","code_1":"EDJ10PROMO","img_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/EDJ_1PACK_TRANSPARENT.png","badge_3":"MOST POPULAR","img_3":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/EDJ_3PACK_TRANSPARENT.png","badge_6":"BEST VALUE","img_6":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/EDJ_6PACK_TRANSPARENT.png","btn_bg_color":"#0e3a27","btn_text_color":"#ffffff","btn_font_size":16,"btn_margin_top":10,"note_text":"Free Shipping over $75+","note_color":"#888888","note_font_size":12,"note_margin_top":12,"bg_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#0e3a27","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40}},"ht_tallow_explained_BG8VgV":{"type":"ht-tallow-explained","blocks":{"item_zDGP4w":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Does it smell like beef?","content":"<p>Not at all. We use only premium, meticulously sourced suet. Our precise, slow-rendering process completely removes the impurities that cause that typical “beefy” kitchen aroma. The result is a clean, completely odorless tallow that lets the pure quality of the ingredient shine through.<\/p>"}},"item_FbWXNw":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Will my skin feeling greasy?","content":"<p>No. Because grass-fed tallow shares the exact same biological profile as your skin’s natural oils (sebum), your skin instantly recognizes it and absorbs it deeply. It goes on rich, but leaves your skin glowing and hydrated - never heavy or greasy. Just remember: a little goes a long way!<\/p>"}},"item_JENQwF":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Will Tallow Cause Acne?","content":"<p>Pure tallow is naturally non-comedogenic, meaning it won’t clog your pores. Instead of suffocating your skin, it gently hydrates and helps balance your natural oil production. Many customers with easily irritated or breakout-prone skin find this pure, 1-ingredient approach actually calms their complexion.<\/p>"}},"item_ieEqzG":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Is it safe for sensitive Skin?","content":"<p>Absolutely. The Everyday Jar was quite literally made for sensitive skin. By eliminating preservatives, alcohols, and synthetic fragrances, we’ve removed the most common triggers for irritation. As with any new skincare product, we simply recommend doing a quick patch test on your inner wrist first.<\/p>"}},"item_3fdkm3":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"What is your shipping and return policy?","content":"<p>We offer <strong>free shipping <\/strong>on all orders over $75+, typically processed within 1 business day. <\/p><p>For more information on our return & refund policy - click <a href=\"\/pages\/refund-policy\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Refund Policy\">here<\/a><\/p>"}},"item_Y6EVpL":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"How long will one Jar  last me?","content":"<p>Because our tallow is 100% active and water-free, a single jar can last <strong>2 to 3 months <\/strong>for daily facial use or about <strong>4 weeks <\/strong>for full-body hydration. Most customers grab two or three at a time so they can keep a dedicated jar for their skincare routine and another for head-to-toe relief.<\/p>"}},"item_DfJCP8":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"What is the shelf life?","content":"<p>Our tallow is shelf-stable for <strong>6 to 12 months<\/strong> when kept in a cool, dry place. <\/p>"}}},"block_order":["item_zDGP4w","item_FbWXNw","item_JENQwF","item_ieEqzG","item_3fdkm3","item_Y6EVpL","item_DfJCP8"],"name":"HT Explained Hub","settings":{"bg_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#0e3a27","sub_heading":"NATURE'S SKIN-NATIVE REMEDY","main_heading":"Tallow Explained"}},"ht_us_vs_them_UTzxtm":{"type":"ht-us-vs-them","blocks":{"us_point_mteyk9":{"type":"us_point","settings":{"text":"100% Regenerative Grass-Fed"}},"them_point_PQhAcq":{"type":"them_point","settings":{"text":"Mass-Produced Industrial Tallow"}},"them_point_NnGcLk":{"type":"them_point","settings":{"text":"Pungent \"Beefy\" Odor"}},"them_point_rPptYr":{"type":"them_point","settings":{"text":"Heavy, Greasy & Clogs Pores"}},"them_point_cJtmWC":{"type":"them_point","settings":{"text":"Leaching Plastic Containers"}},"them_point_hFPBWw":{"type":"them_point","settings":{"text":"Grainy & Inconsistent Texture"}},"us_point_qM79Hm":{"type":"us_point","settings":{"text":"Naturally Odorless & Clean"}},"us_point_4egFhi":{"type":"us_point","settings":{"text":"Bio-Identical Deep Absorption"}},"us_point_nAaPNL":{"type":"us_point","settings":{"text":"Premium